  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Become a Mayhemer and start to make chaos. As a Mayhemer, your goal is to earn Chaos Points and reach the escape area with your teammates before the time runs out. Earn Chaos Points by causing destruction, starting fires, beating people, and more.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Become a Guardian and stop Mayhemers. As a Guardian, your goal is to beat all Mayhemers or stop them from reaching the required Chaos Point until time runs out. Pick up beaten Mayhemers and put them in prison so they will not respawn until they are rescued. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >CREATE CHAOS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cause destruction, start fires, create explosions. Do not let the Guardians stop you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2536260/extras/d3d2c9df90d0091c5e79a636df878029.poster.avif?t=1758661685\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2536260/extras/d3d2c9df90d0091c5e79a636df878029.webm?t=1758661685\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2536260/extras/d3d2c9df90d0091c5e79a636df878029.mp4?t=1758661685\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >STOP THE MAYHEMERS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Stop Mayhemers from causing chaos. Catch them and imprison them.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2536260/extras/647d75206979a9f6d276e687af687d0e.poster.avif?t=1758661685\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2536260/extras/647d75206979a9f6d276e687af687d0e.webm?t=1758661685\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2536260/extras/647d75206979a9f6d276e687af687d0e.mp4?t=1758661685\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Become a Mayhemer and start to make chaos. As a Mayhemer, your goal is to earn Chaos Points and reach the escape area with your teammates before the time runs out. Earn Chaos Points by causing destruction, starting fires, beating people, and more.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Become a Guardian and stop Mayhemers. As a Guardian, your goal is to beat all Mayhemers or stop them from reaching the required Chaos Point until time runs out. Pick up beaten Mayhemers and put them in prison so they will not respawn until they are rescued. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >CREATE CHAOS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cause destruction, start fires, create explosions. Do not let the Guardians stop you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2536260/extras/d3d2c9df90d0091c5e79a636df878029.poster.avif?t=1758661685\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2536260/extras/d3d2c9df90d0091c5e79a636df878029.webm?t=1758661685\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2536260/extras/d3d2c9df90d0091c5e79a636df878029.mp4?t=1758661685\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >STOP THE MAYHEMERS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Stop Mayhemers from causing chaos. Catch them and imprison them.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2536260/extras/647d75206979a9f6d276e687af687d0e.poster.avif?t=1758661685\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2536260/extras/647d75206979a9f6d276e687a